{"tid":2352149,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"繼《煲底之約》後 Tommy 阮民安 又出咗首新歌叫《手足 》大家聽咗未","createTime":"2021-01-03T20:34:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T07:40:13.000Z","uid":384104,"like":8,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4ab7b9d733c13e1dd763e71c916eda5694759a6f","tid":2352149,"uid":384104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T20:34:26.000Z","msg":"大家好 im 光時小男孩 again and again<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n話說Tommy 係19年個陣出咗首歌叫<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">《煲底之約》</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n意在為當時抗爭了五個多月的香港人打氣加油<br />\n<br />\n如歌詞中的 <span class=\"large\">「誰約誓 險境 絕處 都不怕 / 漫天綻放 催淚煙花」「夢中結伴 走過炎夏與冷冬 春風秋雨 / 我會堅持 誓死都不放手」</span><br />\n<br />\n並在歌中寫出香港人期盼<ins><strong>香港重光後 一同在煲底下 脫下面罩相認的心聲</strong></ins><br />\n<span class=\"large\">「捱得過 夜會結束 光輝可映照時代 / 在今世 / 願相約 除罩後見」</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wrczjnLqfZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwrczjnLqfZk&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyTrpXFO54mr1mpDNnesGdkc%3D&h=7641b7c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wrczjnLqfZk</a><br />\n<br />\nMV 中更加係搵咗周庭做女主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋鄺神填詞<br />\n<br />\n而喺今年就再寫咗首歌叫<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">《手足》</span></span><br />\n同樣地都係鄺神填詞<br />\n不過女主角就換咗人啦...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k46qdvt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk46qdvt.jpg&h=e68c184d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_W1w_UwIb54\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_W1w_UwIb54&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyTrpXFO54mr1mpDNnesGdkc%3D&h=24851f67\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_W1w_UwIb54</a><br />\n<br />\nMV 嘅每一句歌詞同每一個嘅晝面都有它意思喺度<br />\n<br />\n好似<span class=\"large\">「手足約定 時代有光 / 下決心 共你撐著過 / 越戰越痛 也要陪著你 這亂世中」「數不清 多少的英勇 / 揮不走 某段沉重傷痛」</span><br />\n<br />\n正如 Tommy 發文提到  :「<strong>2019-20年，是沈默傷痛之年。但香港人沒有屈膝。我們彼此都看到做人的勇氣和高貴。2021年，我們要繼續守著信念，彼此看顧，互相扶持，在各自的位置上，抗戰下去。</strong>」<br />\n<br />\n#不是有希望才堅持 是堅持了才有希望<br />\n# 堅守信念 抗戰到底<br />\n<br />\n所以希望呢首歌可以為你打下氣 而未聽嘅人要快啲去聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而最緊要係記得<span class=\"xx-large\"> <span class=\"red\"> CLS</span></span> 埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外 都想借呢個機會好好多謝片入面嘅人 特別係陳伯 王婆婆 同埋阿 Joy <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感謝你地過去一年一直走在最前面 陪伴 守護我地呢堆小朋友<br />\n<br />\n-所以所以小弟再整合咗個list <br />\n-大家可以嘅梗係喺留言講返聲多謝 再唔係就like 下以示支持啦<br />\n<br />\n1.阮民安 <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tommyboy_ekids/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftommyboy_ekids%2F&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyTrpXFO54mr1mpDNnesGdkc%3D&h=780509f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/tommyboy_ekids/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ekidstommy/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fekidstommy%2F&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyTrpXFO54mr1mpDNnesGdkc%3D&h=43e5ec88\" data-au